            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a little drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>lean beef mince </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Cook for a further 4 min or until cooked through and browned (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1702976394360-x200.jpg",
