        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained noodles</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min or until everything's coated in sauce – this is your <strong>lean beef & sweetcorn stir-fry</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>honey pepper</strong> <strong>peanuts</strong> roughly</p>",
      "order": 7,
