    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lean beef & sweetcorn stir-fry</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>chopped honey pepper peanuts</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave out the peanuts and spring onion!</span></strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
